bio: Creative director @dunmorebeachclub — a new shop in Southampton NY 💫 named a top photographer in the world by @harpersbazaarus.

social_posts.post_text: Weekend made by @popupbagels — so so good, only crumbs left 💫 adding to our summer Saturday routine — pick up available in east Hampton 💥💥 also, hello!
Evening magic 💫 (and the start of umbrella spam!!!😍🥰)
Summer hues in every shade (and a v patient man w a steamer 👀)….more coming soon!!!
A million things to see & love! 😚 (the 🐚 sink!🙆‍♀️)
So in love w these details!!

It’s official! @dunmorebeachclub is now open!!! Come say hi to this dream project with the best team!!! 2 Main Street, southampton NY 💫💫💫💫 Ps we aren’t online yet but we do ship so feel free to DM to shop for inquiries!  Xxxxx

Bling 4 the fing!!!! @emilynixonjewellery is in Southampton today at @dunmorebeachclub with the most beautiful pieces all the way from England!  Each piece is handmade with ocean inspired gemstones and diamonds … best seen in person, come visit 2 main st ✨✨✨✨✨
Ello ello!!! Come tour @dunmorebeachclub summer to fall lewks in stories! Twas hard for me not to bring them all home💘
Our winter wonderland in all her glowy magic !! 🍄✨🍄✨ come see us tomorrow 11-5! 2 main st Southamton !!! ✨✨✨✨✨💯💯💯

Better late than never!!!!!!!!!!! Ornaments up online!!!!! Here are some new beauties to add to your collection 💘 🍊 🐚 ✨💫✨💫💘💘💘 more coming shortly!!!!!!!!!!!! I am particularly enamored by the “plush mush” our latest shroomy wonder and the crispy clam !! Link in bio to our new site @dunmorebeachclub xxxxxxxx!!!!!

@dunmorebeachclub looking extra sparkly and magical for our holiday party last night!!! Thank you to everybody who came! And our five star team behind the scenes, and to all of you for supporting our budding online adventure! 🌟✨🌟✨🌟✨🌟 to many more nights like this!! 🥂🥂🥂🥂
Friends old and new! Like jewelry for your tree 💓💋
